@docs toSvg


## Styling the icon

@docs decorationColor, outline


## Decorations

@docs account, alert, arrowDown, arrowLeft, arrowRight, arrowUp, badge, cancel, check, clock, cog, edit, eye, heart, key, lock, marker, minus, off, plus, refresh, remove, search, send, star, sync


## Opaque types

@docs Icon

